.PP
browse saves file history in \f[V]\[ti]/.browse/browse_files\f[R].
.PP
browse saves command history in \f[V]\[ti]/.browse/browse_shell\f[R].
.PP
browse saves search history in \f[V]\[ti]/.browse/browse_search\f[R].
